<div id="main_content">
	<h2>Cross-Cultural Communication is Key for Middle East-West Relations</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Sonya Dumas
		
		<span class="date">Dec. 9, 2010</span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
	
		
			<div id="related">
				<h3>Related Contacts and Links:</h3>
				<ul>
		
